title: E39 Cocaine Trafficking
itunes:title: Cocaine Trafficking
description:
In this episode, the team discusses cocaine trafficking with war correspondent, documentary filmmaker, and author of "Kilo: Inside the Deadliest Cocaine Cartels - From the Jungles to the Streets", Toby Muse.
